PRINTL Auto-corrections added
PRINTFORML After orgasms exceed a certain amount,「%ANUS_CALL_ENG(VAGINA_CALL_ENG(PENIS_CALL_ENG(CSTR:SWEET_CALL)))%」will be used

;陥落後あなた呼び方は甘えも表示
